data.description: Located at community of Poinciana, Florida! This immaculate single-story gem boasts a separate living room and dining room with chair rail, three spacious bedrooms, two pristine bathrooms, and a laundry room. With a recent top-to-bottom renovation, including a NEW ROOF, new flooring, and new storm screen door, this house is one to see! This thoughtfully designed split floor plan provides privacy and functionality for you and your family. The spacious master bedroom showcases a huge walk-in closet, the master bath has a lovely vanity with a granite countertop, a huge shower with a rain shower head, and impressive floor-to-ceiling tiles. The hall bath is just as remarkable, with a granite vanity, and tub and shower combo with floor-to-ceiling tiles. The well-appointed kitchen will inspire the chef in you as it features granite countertops, a breakfast bar that will be a gathering spot,  42" cabinets, tiled backsplash, and complete stainless steel appliance package- range, dishwasher, and microwave! The kitchen overlooks the spacious family room, or you can step out to the covered lanai, relax, sip, and enjoy the Florida lifestyle, while sitting and watching your 2- and 4-legged babies frolic in the yard. The fresh interior and exterior paint, new appliances, delightful lighting fixtures, and ceiling fans throughout add a modern touch, and the NEW state-of-the-art air conditioning unit makes this house truly move-in ready!.
